titles.title: A bill to extend the temporary suspension of duty on 7-Acetyl-1,1,3,4,4,6-hexamethyltetrahydronaphthalene.

action.text: Sponsor introductory remarks on measure. (CR S4411)
Read twice and referred to the Committee on Finance.

bill.summary: 4/2/1993--Introduced. Amends the Harmonized Tariff Schedule of the United States to extend, through December 31, 1996, the suspension of duty on 7-acetyl-1,1,3,4,4,6-hexamethyltetrahydronaphthalene.
